edits.original_text: Why did he dine to-day, and leave this little creature to the mercy of the cold stones?
edits.corrected_text: Why did he dine to-day, and leave this little creature to the mercy of the cold stones?

edits.original_text: It was a part of her father’s misfortunes that they did.
edits.corrected_text: It was a part of her father’s misfortunes that they did.
